data.description: Welcome to this Modern Brick Two-Unit building with 3 units located in a desirable Austin location! NEW Roof, NEW Siding, NEW Windows, NEW Canopy, NEW Hot Water Tank, NEW Plumbing, NEW Electrical, NEW Flooring, NEW Custom Cabinets, NEW SS Appliances,NEW Doors, Natural Stained Walnut Floors,Tuck Pointing, to much to list. Each unit is large with large bedrooms. Separate Utilities on each floor. Full finished Garden unit with 1 large bedroom. You won't be disappointed. Schedule your showing today! LOW Property Taxes..This building has PASSED the City of Chicago inspection.
